sentences: In 2005, Styles joined Singer/Songwriter Niki Barr as lead guitarist.
After several years of working as a hired guitarist with Barr, the duo formed the "Niki Barr Band" along with bassist Scott Ensign and drummer BJ Kerwin.
The group eventually went on to record several studio albums, including "Bloom" (2008) and "Radar Radio" (2010).
